WEBVTT

00:07.163 --> 00:08.781
<i>Morley: I'm not wrong about Flint.</i>

00:08.832 --> 00:11.483
<i>- To him we're all disposable.
- I don't believe that.</i>

00:11.534 --> 00:14.870
That's because you don't
know about Mrs. Barlow.

00:14.955 --> 00:16.171
You found the schedule.

00:16.256 --> 00:18.507
What if I forgo payment for the schedule

00:18.591 --> 00:20.542
in exchange for my share of the prize?

00:20.627 --> 00:21.961
We'll need some additional items.

00:22.012 --> 00:24.380
<i>- New guns... 12-pounders.
- You'll have it.</i>

00:24.464 --> 00:25.848
Without the Urca we have nothing.

00:25.932 --> 00:28.000
Without Vane we don't have the Urca.

00:28.051 --> 00:30.853
Our friend tried to protect
you. You left anyway.

00:30.937 --> 00:34.506
- Why?
- How did you feel when she threw you aside?

00:34.557 --> 00:36.692
<i>- (Max screaming)
- Eleanor, wait.</i>

00:36.776 --> 00:38.844
(grunting)

00:38.895 --> 00:41.363
<i>Eleanor: Listen to me
carefully. You are finished.</i>

00:41.448 --> 00:44.233
Unless you decide to join
the crew of Captain Flint.

00:44.317 --> 00:45.684
Looks like she just gave us a ship.

00:45.735 --> 00:47.820
Ship with no captain.

00:47.871 --> 00:50.122
- So sorry he did this to you.
- He didn't do this to me.

00:50.189 --> 00:51.657
You did.

